column1: # DATE:     dat - acquisition date of the slide
# STAINING: str - staining of the slide
# ZOOM:     int - approximation of the zoom factor
# WIDTH:    flt - width of slide in cm
# HEIGHT:   flt - height of slide in cm
# PIXELX:   int - number of pixels in width
# PIXELY:   int - number of pixels in height
# SLIDESCANNER: str - slidescanner used to digitize the slide
